Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近變多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好只是小隻的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈巴魯要這種尺寸才有用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個附贈品是哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密探？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她是誰\N接近村子的人都得一死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以做新武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有好菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肝臟很補呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等拿去給魯歐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說她是貴石的主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，Meister GEM呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣，所以把她檢來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個貴石？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將彼此重疊的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖進記憶深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就站在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降臨而下的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地包容一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我訴說著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「守護」的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾度仰望 無限寬闊的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了 那一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量滿溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱切地 強烈地 勇猛地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在沒有光芒的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能感覺到聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有你能發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第19話 宿命的17歲(^^;)\N你們打算做這種事到何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很明顯侵犯了\N加爾德羅貝的主權
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓妳們還可以繼續上課
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該沒什麼問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將身為五柱的“嬌嫣的紫水晶”\N打入牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓持槍的衛兵踐踏\N這應當保持清廉的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況哪裡正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是警衛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在妳們教師群和學生\N都無法使用乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們卻不知道\N黑團潛伏在何處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，相當可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士，請自重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該還有非學不可的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳卻將那個貴石…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃出自我願
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時吾主凪大公也認可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳遲早會後梅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然持有那個貴石
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:05:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王牌當然要最後亮出來\N才叫王牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題，放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會實現你們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你們不背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著只要找到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能湊到真正的王牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，妳醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳差點變成人乾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里…香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:05:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真會苟延殘喘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說這裡是黑谷的村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，這裡挺不錯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被她們檢來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟妳一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說我跟命一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏倒在沙漠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…所謂的黑谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受到詛咒的可怕民族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴放乾淨點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的規則是\N接近村子的人就該死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳別忘了妳的命在我們手中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其對象是妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的公主不就是妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種大騙子說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去叫大夥準備她的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是，頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白，妳等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看她這樣\N現在好歹正常多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛撿到她的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她做什麼都毫無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我，到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們想怎麼處置愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼救她？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳似乎是她的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的不是溫德的女王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情已經不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來妳確實不是什麼當王的料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個幸福的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便亂說，妳這老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳在說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本就沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂正一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻，怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別幫他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是黑谷的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自己站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯歐，你做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的都很喜歡頭領呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說\N她都是我們的頭領嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是黑谷之王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N雖然她確實繼承了前代的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但碧是靠自己的能力\N獲得民眾信賴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過她也付出不少代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等來我房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是要去見那個\N戴眼鏡的大總統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們越過國境了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是愛瑞斯的首都還遠著咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說妳沒自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要認真起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以攔到車的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，就請妳證明一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為這樣人家會停車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更搔首弄姿一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪做得到這麼丟臉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釣到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒，妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是\N愛瑞斯共和國軍國境警衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此以陳列猥褻物\N與擾亂風紀的罪名逮捕妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從畢業紀念舞鬥那一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯跟愛莉卡就失蹤了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳知不知道些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也變得挺寂寥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們一定會沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是回學園比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括畢業舞鬥\N與授予貴石的任命典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一生一世最棒的活躍舞台\N就這麼泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能默不作聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…都好過份…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好不容易…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當上Meister的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要給妳們捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把所有人都捲捲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲捲…捲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆，妳們也來捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色捲捲藍色捲捲黃色捲捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡\N妳為什麼持有那個貴石？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆說，這是媽媽的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…蕾娜或許是我的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，她是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說那是假的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳是與“蒼天的青玉”\N有關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得向妳道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在算起14年…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.71,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，已經15年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們入侵風華宮時的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候還是前代國王在位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了尋求\N藏在地下的某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟黑團一起入侵城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當時\N打算殺害國王的大臣安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在這場戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將蒼天的青玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不顧自己\N已經結婚生子失去力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直到最後一秒\N仍然盡忠於國王勇敢奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在才想道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別弄錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是賭上性命而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強者勝利弱者敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又道什麼歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對黑谷來說，戰爭是尊貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰爭中貫徹自己使命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是敵人，也應予以厚葬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們卻沒守住她的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有從約翰·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個卑鄙男子的手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們原本就不信任那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後\N我們與黑團徹底分道揚鑣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人為什麼那麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道妳們的GEM與奈米機械
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼做出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被如此稱呼，傳說中的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三·姬野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的遺體被保管在\N靈廟地底沉睡的棺木中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為五柱與學生們的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是生出\N珊瑚和珍珠GEM的母體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠生出GEM的母體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須是過去曾為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來生兒育子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為母親的女性身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯那傢伙大概想過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦他得到技術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“蒼天的青玉”，蕾娜·賽雅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能與真祖對抗，成為新主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為全新的乙HiME真祖！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，請看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝研究主任的資料\N幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請加爾德羅貝的女生們\N做點事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後\N任何一位女孩只要希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，就算不希望\N也可以成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事不宜遲，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請妳當負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先招募志願軍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後請妳率領她們去追捕真…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋，你已經康復啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟妮娜還是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會出現判斷錯誤的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，這項任務請交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是體貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要\N挽回名譽的機會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有第二次了喔，懂吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這個星球過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個綠意盎然的美麗行星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是用在十二王戰爭上的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學之力荒廢星球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們黑谷故鄉的“黑色山谷”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一夜之間被失控的兵器消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影響波及到殘存的祖先與其子嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到一種可謂業障的宿疾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們黑谷\N被稱為詛咒之民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭人忌諱厭惡及壓迫的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們見過魯歐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拄著枴杖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經發病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以活不久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀輕輕就得病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強以殘存的科學力\N化身為改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠以活死人的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有加爾德羅貝的奈米機械技術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才有可能治療這種病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在17歲的時候發病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟死了沒兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由這個REM…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析過GEM之後製造出來的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才勉強得以永生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是永遠的17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很諷刺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拯救被科學力打倒的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是只能靠科學的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種不安定\N不知幾時會失控的仿冒品的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到被加爾德羅貝封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類所生出的\N一切智慧與力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對愛莉卡講過對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有科學的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就可以幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再有…戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成全我們的宿願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使多一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或多一份強大力量必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，真白，協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我們蒼天的青玉的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我們Meister-乙HiME的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再當乙HiME了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再使用乙HiME的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領，卡迪亞來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，妳慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.98,0:23:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領妳到底幾歲啊？\N（不要叫我妮依娜）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.05,0:23:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧？我17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領說她17歲就是17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以追究喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
